## Book professional cleaning across Kashmir

Keeping a home or workplace clean takes time — especially before guests, festivals, office inspections, or after renovation dust has settled everywhere. Panun Kaergar connects you with trained cleaning professionals for home deep cleaning and office cleaning across Kashmir, so you book once and know who is coming.

Finding reliable cleaners has often meant informal help without clear standards, supplies, or accountability. Panun Kaergar replaces that guesswork with partner onboarding, customer reviews after completed visits, and booking by phone, WhatsApp, website, or app.

## What cleaning jobs you can book

Residents and small business owners book professional cleaning through Panun Kaergar for one-time deep cleans and scheduled visits. Common requests include:

- Full home deep cleaning — rooms, surfaces, and floors
- Kitchen and bathroom sanitization
- Move-in and move-out cleaning for rented flats
- Sofa, mattress, and carpet cleaning
- Regular housekeeping visits — weekly or bi-weekly
- Office, shop, and clinic cleaning — daily, weekly, or one-time deep cleans
- Post-renovation and post-painting cleanup

Mention property size, service type, and special requests when you book — delicate surfaces, pet areas, nursery rooms, or office equipment zones — so your partner arrives prepared. Most partners bring their own supplies; tell us if you need something specific.

## Why cleaning needs change with Kashmir seasons

Kashmir’s seasons shape when homes and workplaces need a thorough clean. Winter heating and closed windows can leave dust and soot buildup; spring and autumn are popular for seasonal deep cleans; monsoon moisture makes bathroom and kitchen sanitization especially important. After masonry, painting, or carpentry work, fine dust settles in corners that everyday sweeping misses.

Families often book before Eid, weddings, and visits from relatives. Offices, clinics, salons, and shops use Panun Kaergar before audits, inspections, or busy retail periods. Partners on our platform understand residential and small commercial cleaning in local homes and workspaces.

## How to book cleaning with Panun Kaergar

You can book in minutes:

1. **Call** **+91 8899 181 555** to discuss home or office cleaning needs.
2. **WhatsApp** us with your district, property size, and preferred date.
3. Use **[panunkaergar.com/book-a-home-service](/book-a-home-service)** — select **Professional Cleaning** and your area.
4. Open the **Panun Kaergar** customer app, choose **Professional Cleaning**, enter your address, and pick a time slot.

We confirm by call or WhatsApp. In the app you can track your partner until arrival. Pricing depends on property size and service type — estimates appear in the app before you confirm, or your partner can quote after assessing the space.

