## Before your cleaning visit

A few steps help the team work efficiently:

- Clear clutter from floors and surfaces you want cleaned thoroughly.
- Note fragile items, locked rooms, or areas to skip.
- Secure pets if needed, and share access instructions for flats or offices.
- For move-in/move-out or post-renovation jobs, tell us about dust, paint residue, or construction debris in advance.
- Be home, or arrange access so the team can start on time.

